XContentParser.Token token.     while ((token = parser.nextToken()) != null) {         if (token == XContentParser.Token.FIELD_NAME) {             XContentParserUtils.ensureExpectedToken(XContentParser.Token.START_OBJECT, parser.nextToken(), parser::getTokenLocation).             while (parser.nextToken() != XContentParser.Token.END_OBJECT) {                 privileges.add(ApplicationPrivilege.PARSER.parse(parser, null)).             }         }     }     return new GetPrivilegesResponse(new HashSet<>(privileges)). }
